      <title>鳥龜的曬背燈</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/15/turtlelight/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/15/turtlelight/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>鳥龜的曬背燈要含有UVA及UVB，被曬區的溫度介乎攝氏29到32之間為最理想。</p><p><strong>紫外線</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th>種類</th><th>名稱</th><th>波長</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Ultraviolet A (UVA)</td><td>長波紫外線</td><td>320~400n<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1">[1]</a></sup>m</td></tr><tr><td>Ultraviolet B (UVB)</td><td>中波紫外線</td><td>280~320nm</td></tr></tbody></table><p>照射UVB幫助鳥龜產生維他命D3。</p><hr class="footnotes-sep"><section class="footnotes"><ol class="footnotes-list"><li id="fn1" class="footnote-item"><p>nm-nanometre, 1nm = 10<sup>-9</sup>m <a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li></ol></section>]]></content>
      
      
