        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>什麼是WISP？</p><a id="more"></a><p>WISP (Wireless Internet Service Provider)是一種無線路由器設置的模式。這種模式讓路由器變成另一個網絡供應商。</p><blockquote><p>WISP or WISP Client is a mode when a <mark>Wireless port of your Wi-Fi router acts as a WAN port</mark>. If the WISP client mode is available on your wireless router you can configure it to connect to a remote Wi-Fi hotspot and share its Internet connection between the client devices connected via Wi-Fi and Ethernet.</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://wifi-settings.com/wireless-routers/wisp-mode/">wifi-settings.com</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
