      <title>hexo指令</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/01/commands/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/01/commands/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>新增post(draft)</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new draft commands</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>新增post(normal)</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new post bookmarks</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>啟用draft mode來看draft post</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server --draft</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>將draft變成post</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo publish commands</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>#commands是在draft資料夾內.md的名_</p><p><strong>產生webstie交件</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>部署</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>clean有*清除快取檔案 (db.json) 和已產生的靜態檔案 (public)*的作用，所以不用執行<code>hexo generate</code></p><p><strong>部署流程</strong><br>create post-&gt;generate website pages-&gt;deploy</p>]]></content>
      
      
